Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpKamala Harris co-sponsored Bernie Sanders’ $32 trillion-dollar socialist takeover of the entire U.S. healthcare system, which would raise your taxes and bankrupt our country—she supported outlawing all private health insurance that many people have and are extremely happy with—she pledged to give free taxpayer-funded healthcare to ALL illegal aliens, which will destroy our social security system—she sponsored a bill to give illegal aliens taxpayer-funded lawyers— she called for abolishing ICE—she compared ICE agents to members of the KKK—she likened Border Patrol agents to practitioners of human slavery—she voted in favor of deadly Sanctuary Cities—she supports open borders—she opposes even saying the words “illegal alien” and “Radical Islamic Terrorist”—she backs Mass Amnesty and citizenship for all illegals—she supports mandatory gun confiscation, ripping firearms out of the hands of law-abiding citizens
